    <h1>{`CDIP Explainer`}</h1>
    <h2>{`What is a CDIP ?`}</h2>
    <p>{`CDIP stands for Community Development Initiative Proposal. The CDIP is the scoping and framing tool for for anyone interested in contributing to the MakerDAO community initiatives or resources. CDIPs are used to propose new initiatives or expand the scope of `}<a parentName="p" {...{
