    <h3>{`What are the benefits of a CDIP?`}</h3>
    <p>{`The CDIP provides a standard contributing template for Maker’s community. The format provides a few benefits: collect and organize relevant information in a standardized format to make ideas easier to understand, add an efficient and transparent evaluation layer to contribution proposals, simplify the ability to archive ideas and search details about them later, and ultimately serve as a tool to streamline how we review and approve work as a community. CDIPs scale the ability to execute the ideas of the community.`}</p>
