    <h3>{`How does a CDIP Owner ask for resources?`}</h3>
    <p>{`Each CDIP includes a section on costs and resources. As part of the approval process, the owner of the CDIP presents the idea along with the required resources. Resources can include, but not limited to:`}</p>
